text: Eichstätt (German: Landkreis Eichstätt, Bavarian: Landkroas Eichstätt) is a Landkreis (district) in Bavaria, Germany. The district is located in the southern part of the Frankish Alb. 80% of the district is in the Altmühltal Nature Park. ==Towns and municipalities== Towns Municipalities #Beilngries #Eichstätt #Adelschlag #Altmannstein #Böhmfeld #Buxheim #Denkendorf #Dollnstein #Egweil #Eitensheim #Gaimersheim #Großmehring #Hepberg #Hitzhofen #Kinding #Kipfenberg 15.
